==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Overburden
<hw>O"ver*bur`den</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The waste which overlies good
stone in a quarry.</def> <rj><au>Raymond.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Overburdensome</ent>⟦br⟧
